Description:
You find a group of elven refugees arguing with a group or ratmen. When you get close, the leaders of both groups look at you.

They are arguing about who should shelter here. The elves claim that they are not prepared to go deeper into the sewers and the ratmen say that they were here before the elves.

They want to keep it civilized and they hope that you can help them to reach an agreement.
